org.apache.poi.hwmf.record

Class HwmfFill.WmfSetPolyfillMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hwmf.record.HwmfFill.WmfSetPolyfillMode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord, HwmfRecord
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HemfFill.EmfSetPolyfillMode
    Enclosing class:
    HwmfFill 

    public static class HwmfFill.WmfSetPolyfillMode
extends java.lang.Object
implements HwmfRecord
    The META_SETPOLYFILLMODE record sets polygon fill mode in the playback device context for graphics operations that fill polygons.(Meta_SET POYFILLMED记录在播放设备上下文中为填充多边形的图形操作设置多边形填充模式。)

    • Nested Class Summary

      static class  HwmfFill.WmfSetPolyfillMode.HwmfPolyfillMode

    • Field Detail

      • polyFillMode

        protected HwmfFill.WmfSetPolyfillMode.HwmfPolyfillMode polyFillMode
        An unsigned integer that defines polygon fill mode. This MUST be one of the values: ALTERNATE = 0x0001, WINDING = 0x0002(定义多边形填充模式的无符号整数。这必须是其中一个值：ALTERNATE = 0x 0001，WINDING = 0x 0002)
